{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e67ca101dc","title":"公安部关于撤销几个错误文件的通知","origin":"原载《公安建设》1979年第4期，第8-10 页","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5b1c322a50","index":0,"year":1979,"month":1,"day":27,"articleId":"e67ca101dc"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"33b85cb7de","name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"45622f0603","type":"title","text":"公安部关于撤销几个错误文件的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e67ca101dc"},{"id":"fd0e392417","type":"appellation","text":"各省、市、自治区公安局：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e67ca101dc"},{"id":"d77e8de3eb","type":"paragraph","text":"在文化大革命中，谢富治、李震、施义之等秉承林彪、“四人帮”的旨意，为了砸烂公检法，推行林彪、“四人帮”的反革命修正主义路线，炮制了一些错误文件。经过清理，由公安部印发的错误文件主要有：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e67ca101dc"},{"id":"dc13a6ea24","type":"paragraph","text":"一、一九六九年一月八日公安部印发的《关于群众专政的几个典型报告》小册子。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e67ca101dc"},{"id":"e1145e51dc","type":"paragraph","text":"二、一九七四年十二月二十五日公安部《印发上棉十七厂党委关于实行民兵、治保、消防“三位一体”的两个材料的通知》。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e67ca101dc"},{"id":"16a350e9c9","type":"paragraph","text":"三、一九七六年六月施义之在公安局长座谈会上的讲话，《公安局长座谈会纪要（讨论稿）》（有些参加会议的代表抄回去传达了）。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e67ca101dc"},{"id":"648fe429cb","type":"paragraph","text":"对上述文件，予以撤销。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e67ca101dc"},{"id":"264520668a","type":"paragraph","text":"此外，过去公安部发的文件、简报中，属于“两个否定”、“一个砸烂”、推行“三位一体”以及“反击右倾翻案风”等内容，一律废除。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e67ca101dc"},{"id":"8d35cb4603","type":"paragraph","text":" 一九七九年一月二十七日","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e67ca101dc"}],"page":{"id":"71d2bed965","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e67ca101dc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}